{"tid":58845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防巡756迷你倉　三分一違規發1200張警告","createTime":"2016-12-29T07:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T12:11:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23c16c508c756ac62875cf0b26445072b6e1b04d","tid":58845,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161229/photo/bkn-20161229113433752-1229_00822_001_01b.jpg?20161229142420\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161229113433752-1229_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20161229142420&h=27d31f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=wIsT1otLT%2FLa6DRoCHtl%2F38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=a7fa86ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 因應牛頭角時昌迷你倉四級火，政府早前成立跨部門工作小組跟進，並由6月底開始巡查全港的迷你倉及類似處所，檢視有否違反現行法例的規定。署理消防處助理處長(消防安全)曾永鴻表示，巡查後發現至今全港最少有885間迷你倉，當中已完成巡查756間，並向257間違規迷你倉發出1200張消除火警危險通知書，目前有50張已遵辦。他又指，正就相關的安全條例的修例或改例進行工作，但未有詳細資料。<br />\n<br />\n消防處高級消防區長鄭瑞安表示，大部分違規的迷你倉都有多個潛在火警問題，當中迷你倉的排列及布局不當，每列迷你倉的面積過長，令整個布局複雜及迂迴，故規定每列迷你倉不可超過20米長、每個迷你倉的面積不能大於50平方米、倉與倉間的相距為2.4米、間隔板不得超過2.35米高、天花板與儲存物間需留有最少1米距離。<br />\n<br />\n問及迷你倉的規定會在何時推行，曾永鴻指，該規定屬根據現行法例進行，強調並非針對迷你倉，一般倉庫亦受此所限，規定是參考英國的規例而訂。曾又指，現時香港的迷你倉多設在工廈，是較密集的地方，故本地運作不能與其他國家的情況相比較。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161229/bkn-20161229113433752-1229_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=40288125468fa62a0146a996fbde3e98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161229%2Fbkn-20161229113433752-1229_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D40288125468fa62a0146a996fbde3e98&d=wIsT1otLT%2FLa6DRoCHtl%2F38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=f9363ed5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161229/bkn-20161229113433752-1229_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=40288125468fa62a0146a996fbde3e98</a><br />\n<br />\n至於修例方面，曾永鴻表示，由今年6月開始，每個月都會與業界及營運者會面商討，上月底處方更為200多名營運者進行簡介會了解情況，現時處方與業界正就部分方案進行研究，舉例如業界提出倉與倉間的間距過闊，提出可否以其他設施或設備代替，以符合消防條例。問及修例及巡查時間表，曾指暫沒有時間表或詳情可提供"},{"pid":"d53df0927b038bd4532ed8a5b1a757a49479a909","tid":58845,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3172cd0b86d37581f4eb92e432a884e5d6decf3","tid":58845,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:40:47.000Z","msg":"睇咗759<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b306a00437131090bdf04791a8d24f435d4fa8","tid":58845,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"睇錯759迷你倉 心諗肥佬幾時搞過呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7daf1053ee736bd1f8e30b746af04765eaf01a70","tid":58845,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990d148065871ca6c5803fa40bcafbdbb9dacec7","tid":58845,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"屌 睇左759<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044401f6854e98fac1c5c18a67b513b8128e1fd5","tid":58845,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"唔死人唔做野"},{"pid":"2b882683545c57716f0d1809d35c0d9885fca140","tid":58845,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"心諗乜759開左迷你倉咩"},{"pid":"3113b131cb5fa9b6a4b2d1c3a8a7ac3a72c2910a","tid":58845,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 睇左759<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想講 好難唔睇錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}